## ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
## .gitignore for a C# / .NET / Visual Studio (WinForms) solution
## CourseEnrollmentSystem
## ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

## ----- Build output -----
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
[Ww][Ii][Nn]32/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
bld/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

## ----- Visual Studio cache / user-specific files -----
.vs/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.suo
*.userprefs
*.sln.docstates
*.VC.db
*.VC.VC.opendb

## ----- MSTest / vstest / test results -----
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## ----- NuGet -----
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
**/[Pp]ackages/*
!**/[Pp]ackages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/

## ----- Roslyn / build cache -----
*.GhostDoc.xml
.ntvs_analysis.dat
[Bb]in[Ll]og/
*.binlog

## ----- ReSharper / Rider / other IDE caches -----
_ReSharper*/
*.[Rr]e[Ss]harper
*.DotSettings.user
.idea/

## ----- Debugger / minidump / crash files -----
*.dmp
*.pdb

## ----- Publish / ClickOnce -----
publish/
*.publishsettings
PublishScripts/
*.azurePubxml
*.pubxml
*.publishproj

## ----- App secrets / local config overrides -----
appsettings.*.local.json
*.local.config
secrets.json

## ----- OS junk files -----
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

## ----- SQL Server / database files (if a local .mdf ever gets created) -----
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.ndf

## ----- Editor swap / backup files -----
*~
*.swp
*.bak
*.tmp
